Usage: SET STATUS_UPTIME <text of display for status line uptime>
  The value of STATUS_UPTIME is replaced in the STATUS_FORMAT
  variable for any occurrence of %1. The STATUS_UPTIME may
  contant a %d which is replaced by number of days, %h which
  is replaced by number of hours or %m which is replaced by
  number of minutes your client has been running.
